item.title: Compiling Problem
item.dc:creator: @Aurai Aurai
item.description:
@Aurai wrote:

It only updates the changes you make in the code.
The compiler checks for errors in your programming and makes your new code runnable.

If you haven’t edited your server, it wont change when you compile it.
